attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a NavVis M6 machine in order to clean it. They open the box and remove the parts, including the wheels and the camera. They attach the wheels back onto the base and reassemble the machine. Finally, they clean the camera lenses and submit the machine.

attributes.Transcription: Now, you can go and grab that cloth from the table.
